However, it is really important to prepare how to
end it.

235
00:08:43.100 --> 00:08:45.090
It is recommended that the patient and the family
talk together and

236
00:08:45.090 --> 00:08:45.422
prepare the

237
00:08:45.422 --> 00:08:47.080
last part of their life in the way they want.

238
00:08:47.700 --> 00:08:51.060
I would like to share my experience as a nurse.

239
00:08:51.700 --> 00:08:54.340
I watched the end of many patients.

240
00:08:54.520 --> 00:08:58.628
Some families are really good at preparing, so I saw
the patient

241
