go to the hospital peacefully.

242
00:09:00.340 --> 00:09:06.420
However, in some cases, even though the patient is
suffering too much,

243
00:09:06.420 --> 00:09:09.684
because of the hope that the family will live a
little more,

244
00:09:09.684 --> 00:09:10.228
I saw

